snippet.title: SRW X-Ω - Mega Man Debut PV (Rockman)[スパロボxω ロックマン 新規参戦]
snippet.description:
To commemorate Mega Man's 30th Anniversary, Mega Man will be making his SRW debut in 2018. During the limited timed Mega Man event, Mega Man, Proto Man and Bass will be obtainable and they will have voiced parts as well. In addition, the 8 robot masters from Mega Man 2 will be obtainable as well. All these Mega Man units will come in their 8-bit sprite form.
